Armadyl helmet (or) is a temporary piece of content found only in unrestricted worlds.
The contents of this page refer to a piece of content only available on temporary unrestricted worlds as a means to test it before release.
Its design is subject to change, and the graphics are used as a placeholder.

The Armadyl helmet (or) is an Armadyl helmet with an Armadyl armour ornament kit attached to it. Doing so makes it untradable and it is a cosmetic upgrade providing no additional bonuses. It can be dismantled at any time returning both parts back to the player.
